## Required Fields

| Field | Required | Notes |
|-------|----------|-------|
| `tags` | Yes | Must include `type/`, `project/`, `stage/` |
| `lead` | Yes | One-line summary for callouts |
| `icon` | Yes | Emoji for visual scanning |
| `created` | Yes | ISO date |
| `modified` | Yes | Update on every edit |
| `template.name` | Yes | Source template name |
| `template.stage` | Yes | Folder stage number |
| `project` | Yes | Project name |
| `status` | Yes | active/paused/completed/archived |

