## Linking Rules

1. Use WikiLinks: `[[Note Name]]`
2. Use display text for clarity: `[[Long Note Name|Short]]`
3. Link to headings: `[[Note#Heading]]`
4. Embed canvases: `![[Canvas.canvas]]`
5. Use inline Dataview fields: `**Source**:: [[Note]]`

## Callout Usage

Display frontmatter in callouts:

```markdown
> [!note] `= this.icon` Title
> `= this.lead`
```

## File Naming

- Use Title_Case with underscores: `Market_Overview.md`
- Prefix with stage number in templates: `03_PRD.md`
- Canvas files match note names: `UX_Flow.md` â†’ `UX_Flow.canvas`

## Do NOT

- Create notes without frontmatter
- Use tags not in the taxonomy
- Leave `modified` date unchanged after edits
- Create orphan notes (no links to/from)
- Duplicate content across notes (link instead)
